to call you Kuma?

00:12:38.091 --> 00:12:38.842 position:50% align:center
Wha--?

00:12:38.925 --> 00:12:41.428 position:50% align:center
[yelps] I apologize!

00:12:41.511 --> 00:12:45.015 position:50% align:center
