where the line is.

00:13:50.830 --> 00:13:52.749 position:50% align:center
So don't worry about me.

00:13:52.832 --> 00:13:56.336 position:50% align:center
On that subject, when you
got fired the last time,

00:13:56.419 --> 00:13:58.755 position:50% align:center
what made you punch your boss?

00:13:58.838 --> 00:14:03.343 position:50% align:center
[KUMATANI] Well, I was just
kinda pissed about something.

00:14:03.426 --> 00:14:05.845 position:50% align:center
Enough to give up your job?

00:14:08.890 --> 00:14:12.352 position:50% align:center
[EDEI] Shooting's about
to start. Stand by.

00:14:12.435 --> 00:14:14.646 position:50% align:center
[ALL]
Got it.

00:14:14.729 --> 00:14:18.942 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI] <i>Konnichiwa</i> !
How's everybody doing today?

00:14:19.025 --> 00:14:22.320 position:50% align:center
