ready for the ABC Exerci--

00:14:22.404 --> 00:14:24.489 position:50% align:center
Hey, Uramichi Oniisan!

00:14:24.572 --> 00:14:26.866 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
Hm? What can I do for you?

00:14:26.950 --> 00:14:29.869 position:50% align:center
Can you tell me what
"harassment" means?

00:14:31.371 --> 00:14:32.831 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
Well, you know,

00:14:32.914 --> 00:14:35.583 position:50% align:center
it isn't quite that
easy to pin down.

00:14:35.667 --> 00:14:38.795 position:50% align:center
