Hey, Kumatani, when's our cue?

00:17:21.541 --> 00:17:23.835 position:50% align:center
[KUMATANI]
Just stay asleep till you die.

00:17:23.918 --> 00:17:26.629 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA] That's awful.
You're being verbally abusive.

00:17:26.713 --> 00:17:28.089 position:50% align:center
That's power harassment.

00:17:28.173 --> 00:17:30.925 position:50% align:center
[KUMATANI] It's mobbing.
